com.codename1.io
Class JSONParser

java.lang.Object
  com.codename1.io.JSONParser
All Implemented Interfaces:
JSONParseCallback
public class JSONParser
extends java.lang.Object
implements JSONParseCallback

Fast and dirty parser for JSON content on the web, it essentially returns a Hashtable object mapping the object fields to their values. If the value is a nester object a nested hashtable is returned.
